<lyrics>[V1]
 1- wqt lmạ tkwn ṣʿạby .. ḥạjbẗ ʿn ʿyny ạlsmạ
 wạlqy̱ nfsy fy ạ̹ḍṭrạby .. byn ḥqạyq mw̉lmẗ
 ạ̹nt wḥdk tstṭyʿ yạ yswʿ .. tyjy wtfyḍ bạlslạm
 ạ̹nt yạ ḥṣny ạlmnyʿ yạ yswʿ .. ạ̉qwy̱ m ạlkẖwf wạlẓlạm
 2- wqt lmạ tkwn jbạly .. wạqfẗ ḍdy bmstḥyl
 wạlsẖkwk tnhsẖ fy bạly .. myn ysẖyl ḥmly ạltqyl
 ạ̹nt wḥdk tstṭyʿ yạ yswʿ .. tyjy tnql ạljbạl
 ạ̹nt yạ ḥṣny ạlmnyʿ yạ yswʿ .. klmtk fwq ạlmḥạl
 3- wqt lmạ ạlshl yṣʿb .. wạlḥạjạt tṭrḥ fsẖl
 lmạ wʿd ạlnạs byhrb .. wạlʿml kẖạb wạlạ̉ml
 ạ̹nt wḥdk tstṭyʿ yạ yswʿ .. trd jwạyạ ạlly ḍạʿ
 wạlly yṣʿb ʿ ạljmyʿ yạ yswʿ .. ybqy̱ ʿndk mstṭạʿ</lyrics>
<title>wḥdk tstṭyʿ</title>
</song>